  "description": {
    "main": "The Sonos Arc Ultra fills every inch of your room with sound. On-board are 14 Sonos-engineered drivers and Sound Motion technology for clear, deep, and balanced sound. It's also incredibly precise, placing sound all around you for a true-to-life experience. Dolby Atmos adds another dimension to movies and shows, enveloping you in a 9.1.4 spatial audio experience. You'll feel like the action is happening all around you, just like the cinema.",
    "goodToKnow": [
      "A centre channel and AI Speech Enhancement boost dialogue, so you never miss a word.",
      "The curved shape, low-profile design, and matte finish all add to the minimalist, iconic looks.",
      "You can control the Arc Ultra using your TV remote, the Sonos app, touch controls, or voice commands.",
      "Trueplay optimises the audio based on where you place the sound bar in the room."
